flowchart LR
  Client[Client / ShopBack App] -->|REST| API[NestJS API]

  API -->|Prisma| PG[(Postgres)]
  API -->|Tx write| OUTBOX[(OutboxEvent)]
  OUTBOX -->|poll| Publisher[Worker: Outbox Publisher]
  Publisher -->|Kafka produce| RP[(Redpanda / Kafka)]
  RP -->|Kafka consume| Consumer[Worker: Consumer]
  Consumer -->|upsert| INBOX[(InboxEvent)]
  Consumer -->|process| Ledger[(LedgerEntry)]
  Consumer -->|fail| Retry[Retry Loop\n(backoff + attempts)]
  Retry -->|reprocess| Ledger
  Retry -->|max attempts| DLQ[(DLQ Topic)]

  subgraph Observability
    Logs[JSON Logs + requestId/correlationId]
  end
  API -.-> Logs
  Publisher -.-> Logs
  Consumer -.-> Logs
